languages.text: "Что... это такое?! Голоса все вопят, рыдают, задыхаются — перед нами воплощенная смерть!"
"What is that? The voices... they're screaming, wailing, choking! We're up against death itself!"

languages.text: « Qu'est-ce que c'est que ça ? Les voix... Elles hurlent, elles se lamentent, elles s'étouffent ! Nous sommes face à la mort elle-même ! »
languages.original_text: "What is that? The voices... they're screaming, wailing, choking! We're up against death itself!"

languages.text: "Was ist das? Die Stimmen ... sie schreien, kreischen, röcheln! Wir kämpfen gegen den Tod selbst!"
languages.original_text: "What is that? The voices... they're screaming, wailing, choking! We're up against death itself!"

languages.text: “那是什么东西？那些声音……它们在尖叫，在哭泣，在窒息！我们面对的东西，恐怕就是死亡本身！”
languages.original_text: "What is that? The voices... they're screaming, wailing, choking! We're up against death itself!"

languages.text: «¿Qué es eso? Las voces... gritan, gimen, ¡se ahogan! ¡Nos enfrentamos a la misma muerte!».
languages.original_text: "What is that? The voices... they're screaming, wailing, choking! We're up against death itself!"

traits.locale_text: «¿Qué es eso? Las voces... gritan, gimen, ¡se ahogan! ¡Nos enfrentamos a la misma muerte!».

languages.text: 「何なのあれ？声が…叫んで、嘆いて、むせび泣いている！敵は死そのものだわ！」

languages.text: "Ne oluyor? Sesler... Çığlıklar, feryatlar, boğuk iniltiler! Ölümle karşı karşıyayız!"
